  ('optician-moex-02739', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '採用視網膜檢影鏡時，檢影鏡光束線條放在 90 度時測得-3.50DS，檢影鏡光束線條放在 180 度時測得 -2.50DS，請問患者的矯正度數為何？', '["-2.50DS/-1.00DC × 090°", "-2.50DS/-1.00DC × 180°", "-3.50DS/-1.00DC × 090°", "-3.50DS/-1.00DC × 180°"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02740', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '眼鏡配戴者右眼近視-6.00DS，左眼近視-8.00DS，雙眼瞳距66 mm，其右眼瞳距34 mm及左眼瞳距32 mm。 眼鏡的雙眼鏡片光心之間的距離（DBOC）為66 mm，其中右眼瞳距30 mm及左眼瞳距36 mm。請問配 戴眼鏡會產生多少的雙眼水平稜鏡量（△）？', '["0.6△BO（base out，基底朝外）", "0.6△BI（base in，基底朝內）", "0.8△BI（base in，基底朝內）", "0.8△BO（base out，基底朝外）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02741', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一光學十字處方：最正的軸在090度屈光度+4.00D，最負的軸在180度屈光度+2.50D，請解析驗光處 方為下列何者？', '["+2.50DS/+1.50DC × 090°", "-1.50DS/+2.50DC × 090°", "+4.00DS/+1.50DC × 180°", "+2.50DS/+1.50DC × 180°"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02742', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於遠視合併散光配鏡處方可以有不同的表示形式，因為球柱透鏡可以拆解為球面透鏡及圓柱透鏡，請 問下列何者的處方實際屈光度與其他三者不同？', '["+5.50DS/+2.00DC × 090°", "+3.50DS/-2.00DC × 090°", "+1.50DS/+2.00DC × 180°", "+3.50DC × 180°/+1.50DC × 090°"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02743', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一副眼鏡具有兩片球面凸透鏡片，且配戴者瞳孔間距離（interpupillary distance, PD）小於兩眼矯正鏡片 光心之間的距離（DBOC），當配戴者戴上此副眼鏡往正前方直視，此時會產生那一種稜鏡效應？', '["基底朝內", "基底朝外", "基底朝上", "基底朝下"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02744', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '視網膜檢影鏡之工作距離，指的是患者的眼睛到視網膜檢影鏡的距離。當工作距離拉長到為67公分時， 檢影用屈光度為-5.00DS/-2.00DC × 180°，請問實際屈光度數為何？', '["-5.00DS/-2.00DC × 180°", "-6.50DS/-2.00DC × 180°", "-5.75DS/-2.00DC × 180°", "-6.50DS/-3.50DC × 180°"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02745', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '交替遮蓋測驗（alternating cover test），首先要病患先看著手上的注視物，若用遮蓋板遮住右眼觀察左眼， 發現左眼並不會移動，然後遮蓋板移去遮蓋左眼觀察右眼，發現右眼會移動，再來，遮蓋板移開左眼觀 察右眼，發現右眼並不會移動，其最適當的診斷為何？', '["右眼經常性斜視", "左眼經常性斜視", "交替性斜視", "右眼隱藏性斜視"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
